{"pin":"BH01052","subcodes":[{"code":"BH01052","anchor":"","first_line":"This is a Book wherein is mentioned that which causeth tears to flow from the eyes of them that are near unto God. O Pen! Make mention of that which hath befallen the Remembrance [3.5s]... ...God is My witness, O people! I was asleep on My couch, when lo, the Breeze of God wafting over Me roused Me from My slumber.","first_line_orig":"هذا کتاب فیه یذکر ما یجری عنه الدموع من اعین المقربین ان یا قلم فاذکر ما ورد علی ذکر  ","language":"1","word_count":"800","subjects":"@rejection by the people of the Bayan, @Manifestation of God does not act of own volition, @Baha'u'llah in Sulaymaniyyih, @self-concealment of the Manifestation of God, @detachment; severance; renunciation; patience","notes":" \u003ca href=\"http://web.archive.org/web/20070930181707/http://bahai-library.com/resources/leiden.list/leiden.list.html#379\"\u003eLL#379\u003c/a\u003e","translations":[],"writing_refs":[{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"ar","lang_name":"Arabic"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"fa","lang_name":"Persian"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"nl","lang_name":"Dutch"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"ro","lang_name":"Romanian"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"ta","lang_name":"Tamil"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"vi","lang_name":"Vietnamese"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"el","lang_name":"Greek"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"es","lang_name":"Spanish"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"fr","lang_name":"French"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"hu","lang_name":"Hungarian"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"ja","lang_name":"Japanese"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"pl","lang_name":"Polish"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","la